Billy I want you to move
the laptop around, ok?

554
00:56:29,286 --> 00:56:31,654
Just move the laptop around so
I can see the rest of the room,
go on.

555
00:56:31,655 --> 00:56:34,156
Please?

556
00:56:34,157 --> 00:56:35,091
Keep moving...

557
00:56:36,059 --> 00:56:37,526
keep moving the laptop.

558
00:56:37,527 --> 00:56:38,160
That's it.
Good boy.

559
00:56:40,230 --> 00:56:40,296
keep moving some more...

560
00:56:41,732 --> 00:56:42,098
that's it...

561
00:56:43,533 --> 00:56:43,833
just need to see the...

562
00:56:44,902 --> 00:56:45,501
the room.

563
00:56:48,171 --> 00:56:49,138
What is that?

564
00:56:56,680 --> 00:56:58,080
Billy...

565
00:56:58,081 --> 00:56:59,482
BILLY!

566
00:56:59,483 --> 00:57:00,883
