have the bed.

585
00:59:40,544 --> 00:59:41,944
No it's alright.

586
00:59:41,945 --> 00:59:43,345
I'll be ok.

587
00:59:43,346 --> 00:59:44,747
No.

588
00:59:44,748 --> 00:59:46,148
No, no, please.

589
00:59:46,149 --> 00:59:48,551
You won't.

590
00:59:48,552 --> 00:59:49,819
Mr Williams, I want to talk to
you about this again in the
morning.

591
