674
01:07:15,565 --> 01:07:15,931
Ok, I'll get it done, promise.

675
01:07:19,903 --> 01:07:21,537
I'll even drop it down to you
when it's done, Ok?

676
01:07:24,807 --> 01:07:26,341
Look...

677
01:07:26,342 --> 01:07:29,444
I've been thinking...

678
01:07:29,445 --> 01:07:29,878
