682
01:07:55,972 --> 01:07:58,840
If anyone walks here tonight,
we'll see their footsteps

683
01:07:58,841 --> 01:08:00,342
It's like snow!

684
01:08:00,343 --> 01:08:01,743
Can I have a go?

685
01:08:01,744 --> 01:08:03,445
Yeah!

686
01:08:04,314 --> 01:08:07,249
Now no one can get in without
us knowing.

687
01:08:27,637 --> 01:08:31,673
You're like me

688
