What's with all the powder,
Dave?

689
01:09:59,295 --> 01:10:01,763
It's flour from the kitchen.

690
01:10:01,764 --> 01:10:03,165
Oh..

691
01:10:03,166 --> 01:10:04,566
is that right?

692
01:10:04,567 --> 01:10:06,501
What's with all the flour,
are you making a cake?

693
01:10:06,502 --> 01:10:08,637
What do you want?

694
01:10:08,638 --> 01:10:10,038
Get your clothes on.

695
01:10:10,039 --> 01:10:10,839
You're coming with me.

696
01:10:15,044 --> 01:10:15,644
We found a hammer in the canal,
with your fingerprints on it.

697
01:10:19,549 --> 01:10:20,015
A hammer that belonged to your
wife's lover.

698
01:10:24,020 --> 01:10:27,255
He says it went missing
the night she disappeared.

699
01:10:27,256 --> 01:10:27,989
Can you explain that?

700
01:10:31,761 --> 01:10:33,161
There was a murder in my house
in..

701
01:10:33,162 --> 01:10:35,997
in 1902.

702
01:10:35,998 --> 01:10:37,566
What...

703
01:10:37,567 --> 01:10:38,333
You could look all of this is
up; and a man killed his whole
family.

704
01:10:41,838 --> 01:10:43,638
You understand me...

705
01:10:43,639 --> 01:10:45,640
and I think he was the one who
did it.

706
01:10:45,641 --> 01:10:46,241
I have proof, I've captured
something on film.

707
01:10:49,645 --> 01:10:51,046
It's a ghost.

708
01:10:54,684 --> 01:10:56,084
You can see it in a few days.

709
01:10:58,454 --> 01:10:59,087
As the senior welfare officer I
have no choice but to recommend
his case to social

710
01:11:03,259 --> 01:11:06,194
services and recommend that
the child is taken into care.

711
