people react differently to the
death of a loved one

716
01:11:24,547 --> 01:11:32,547
and, by the way, this is the
same nanny that Mr Williams
caught smoking drugs in her
room, so...

717
01:11:45,701 --> 01:11:48,003
No way!

718
01:11:48,004 --> 01:11:49,404
No way!!

719
01:11:49,405 --> 01:11:51,973
Yes.

720
01:11:51,974 --> 01:11:55,243
Yes, we can do that.

721
01:11:55,244 --> 01:11:57,612
We'll wait for the report back
from the psychiatrist and then
we'll see what to do after that.

722
01:12:03,653 --> 01:12:05,554
I'm not going to a
psychiatrist.

723
01:12:05,555 --> 01:12:07,022
There's nothing wrong with me.

724
01:12:07,023 --> 01:12:08,423
You have to.

725
01:12:08,424 --> 01:12:09,457
We agreed to it.

726
01:12:09,458 --> 01:12:10,892
You did.
I didn't.

727
01:12:10,893 --> 01:12:11,927
I'm not going.

728
