732
01:12:29,512 --> 01:12:34,649
Don't look.

733
01:12:39,655 --> 01:12:45,560
Don't look.

734
01:12:49,165 --> 01:12:51,032
Is there somebody outside?

735
01:12:54,270 --> 01:12:55,670
No.

736
01:12:55,671 --> 01:12:57,606
Dad..

737
01:13:00,843 --> 01:13:03,712
What?

738
01:13:03,713 --> 01:13:05,680
