hardly recognised your voice.

759
01:18:12,688 --> 01:18:13,288
You were crying.

760
01:18:17,359 --> 01:18:21,095
You said you wanted to
tell me something about Alice.

761
01:18:23,465 --> 01:18:24,799
That wasn't me.
I didn't call you.

762
01:18:28,637 --> 01:18:29,237
Sit down.

763
01:18:35,277 --> 01:18:39,681
If you did hurt her, if you
did do it, maybe you should
just...

764
01:18:43,485 --> 01:18:47,956
